Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Atomic Energy Community, and in particular the second paragraph of Article 101 thereof,
Whereas the Framework Agreement for scientific and technical cooperation between the European Communities and the Republic of Iceland (1) was signed on 30 October 1989;
Whereas by Council Decision of 19 June 1989, the Council approved this Framework Agreement for the purposes of final conclusion by the Commission on behalf of the European Atomic Energy Community;
Whereas this Framework Agreement should be finally concluded on behalf of the European Atomic Energy Community;
